No. 901,

October Term, 1940.

Bakery & Pastry Drivers & Helpers Local 802 of the International Brotherhood of Teamsters et al. v. Wohl et al. October 20, 1941. Mr. Edward C. Maguire for petitioners. Hyman Wohl and Louis Platzman, pro se.

The petition for rehearing is granted. The judgment entered June 2,1941,313 U. S. 548, is vacated and the mandate is recalled.
